# Sparky HQ Images Directory

Store brand-specific images here:
- Logos (logo.png, logo-white.png, favicon.ico)
- Hero images (hero-home.jpg, hero-services.jpg)
- Service images (panel-upgrade.jpg, ev-charger.jpg, emergency.jpg)
- Tool screenshots (ev-sizer.png, panel-planner.png)
- Team photos (electrician-*.jpg)

Images will be automatically deployed to staging/production via GitHub Actions.

## Usage in Patterns

Reference images in pattern HTML files:
```html
<img src="/infra/wordpress/brands/sparky-hq/assets/images/logo.png" alt="Sparky HQ Logo" />
```

## Image Guidelines

- **Formats:** PNG (logos), JPG (photos), SVG (icons)
- **Optimization:** Compress before committing (use tools like TinyPNG, ImageOptim)
- **Naming:** Use kebab-case (e.g., `hero-home.jpg`, `service-panel-upgrade.jpg`)
- **Sizes:** Optimize for web (typically < 500KB per image)

